{"tid":2488447,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子反國安法遊行非法集結罪成 羅德泉今判處監禁3個月","createTime":"2021-04-14T08:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T11:12:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a942813d2c18dcb13bbf311986064cf16d5c6d60","tid":2488447,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:45:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15030&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvpo9Jm%2BrpizTNr1X5Fgg%2Fao%3D&h=519986df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15030</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#羅德泉主任裁判官<br />\n#20200524銅鑼灣<br />\n#判刑<br />\n<br />\n陳 (29)  🛑已還押16日<br />\n<br />\n控罪：參與非法集結<br />\n被控於2020年5月24日，在銅鑼灣軒尼詩道與怡和街交界連同其他身分不詳人士參與非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n索取背景報告正面，被告同意內容。辯方律師呈上一封由李姓牧師撰寫新求情信，表示被告在收押時有深切反省，並希望修讀神學，將來貢獻社會。<br />\n<br />\n🔥判刑速報<br />\n即時監禁3個月❗️❗️"},{"pid":"883177c9f89401d378831630c0fbf0c6f681656d","tid":2488447,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26342c0d8263136ef2dc4b9e4de30d2d3ad1ab0f","tid":2488447,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff35ef190fc8521314a9046525b717efd9f16e1","tid":2488447,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdee62ea4aa44553324df8e3da659a3cd1787e8","tid":2488447,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:58:28.000Z","msg":"羅狗"},{"pid":"542568048aa72bf5ae67f49441ff75374cd1f827","tid":2488447,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da7ec68127daf0faa1a5e7b2c5d0b5a5b66f509","tid":2488447,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:09:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b7a7a55cb6d79bd7af65f7cd3bc4e85798681c","tid":2488447,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:38:46.000Z","msg":"主任裁判官羅德泉指被告在集結行動中雖然不是主導者，但仍屬主要角色，因集結可以團結力量，壯大聲勢，令在場人士情緒高漲，而有膽量作出平常不敢做的行為。羅官指，根據片段被告只是「四圍行，無掟嘢」，在考慮所有情況後以4個半月作量刑起點，認罪扣減3分1刑期，今於東區裁判法院判被告即時監禁3個月。<br />\n<br />\n羅官表示，本案的集結不是單獨事件，並非與其他地方的集結案無關。現場人士集結在一起，一同起哄及聲勢浩大，以達到協同目的，有膽量作出堵路及破壞等行為；另指案發當日灣仔及銅鑼灣一帶有嚴重保安問題，有人堵路及縱火等。羅官續指，此類案件被告多為年輕人，大多沒有刑事案底，但仍屬重要角色，因為如果集結人士不出席聚集，即使號召者再努力仍難以成事。"},{"pid":"cfc9f6ae7fb8279b737cdaa34d25bc65536a40bf","tid":2488447,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"主任裁判官羅德泉指，雖然被告不是集結的主導者，但參與者也是重要角色，又指「集結主要在聲勢浩大下，參與者情緒高漲做出一啲平日唔敢做嘅事情」，如堵路等暴力行為；<span class=\"red\">若沒有他們出席，「號召者點努力都難以成事</span>」。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/5-24-%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-29%E6%AD%B2%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%B7%A5%E8%AA%8D%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A3-3-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%98-%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E8%80%85%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F5-24-%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-29%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%259B%25A3-3-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%2589%25B2%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvpo9Jm%2BrpizTNr1X5Fgg%2Fao%3D&h=c80366c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F5-24-%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-29%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%259B%25A3-3-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%2589%25B2%2F&h=83f42027\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/5-24-%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-29%E6%AD%B2%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%B7%A5%E8%AA%8D%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A3-3-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%98-%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E8%80%85%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2/</a>"},{"pid":"452f073c269a1a13f5bd25000b4a3772fc0d2763","tid":2488447,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d777cf684467fad59c45995e49a1b161069563","tid":2488447,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:13:59.000Z","msg":"網民於去年5月發起在港島區示威，反對當局強推國安法及國歌法，其間會計軟件銷售員當天在場揮動「光復香港 時代革命」旗幟，事後被捕。涉案銷售員早前承認參與非法集結，主任裁判官羅德泉今判刑指，被告雖非集結主導者，但單是參與集結也能團結力量，壯大聲勢，示威者在情緒高漲下便會「做出一啲平常唔敢去做嘅行為」，終判監三個月。<br />\n<br />\n羅官續指，被告雖然不是集結的主導者或召集人，但參與集結也能團結力量，示威者在聲勢浩大下情緒高漲，便會「做出一啲平常唔敢去做嘅行為」，例如堵路和行使暴力，而作出有關行為者多數是沒有案底、具備正當職業或仍在學的年輕人。羅官又認為，若缺乏他人參與，縱使號召者如何努力也難以成事。<br />\n<br />\n羅官考慮到被告只是在現場走動，沒有投擲物品等行為，以監禁四個半月作量刑起點，在認罪扣減三分之一刑期後，判被告監禁三個月。被告原本另被控展示煽動刊物罪，羅官今應控方申請，控罪撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/A3WDG3RGB5H3THFUIQMIMDHRS4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FA3WDG3RGB5H3THFUIQMIMDHRS4%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvpo9Jm%2BrpizTNr1X5Fgg%2Fao%3D&h=d135ba56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FA3WDG3RGB5H3THFUIQMIMDHRS4%2F&h=c645107a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/A3WDG3RGB5H3THFUIQMIMDHRS4/</a>"},{"pid":"2c218a121e1d90f6d3fda2055b30b4dfd5100313","tid":2488447,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf6fc4167a945367c99177010e0c64d6ffa97bd","tid":2488447,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6e16adf9ed2db11b283f5191dcf0401368535b","tid":2488447,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}